“all she does is make silly videos” were more or less the comment I heard someone make about me. Well making these “silly” videos is what let me quit my 9-5 and live the life I desired, one where I get to decide what my day looks like, spend time with my family and friends, financial freedom to live in the home I like 💌 

no offence to anyone who genuinely enjoys a corporate job, I think it’s great, I can say it cause I did one for a long time, but this is the life I chose and it’s always been the right call 🫶🏻💓

it was this day that kick started my journey into the content creation space when one of our reels went viral 💓
